NAME
	write - send a message to a user

SYNOPSIS
	void write(string message)

DESCRIPTION
	Send 'message' to this_player().  The message may contain
	color codes, as described in /doc/misc/ansi_colors.  Any color
	codes in string message are translated into ansi color codes,
	the message is wrapped, and than it is sent to this_player().

SEE ALSO
	afun/out, afun/out_unmod

